msgid "Should be set to around 98% of your available upload bandwidth. Entering a number which is too high will result in QoS not meeting its class requirements. Entering a number which is too low will needlessly penalize your upload speed. You should use a speed test program (with QoS off) to determine available upload bandwidth. Note that bandwidth is specified in kbps, leave blank to disable update QoS. There are 8 kilobits per kilobyte."
